##Phase 1 and 2 Test File##

// This file tests all Phase 1 and Phase 2 features

##Task States - Level 0##

[ ] Unchecked task - this is pending
[•] In progress task - actively working on this
[√] Completed task with checkmark
[x] Completed task with x
[!] Urgent task - needs attention now
[-] Skipped task - decided not to do
[.] On hold task - paused for now
[+] Added task - newly added
[?] Question task - needs clarification

##Task States - Level 1 (4 spaces)##

    [ ] Level 1 unchecked task
    [•] Level 1 in progress task
    [√] Level 1 completed task
    [x] Level 1 completed with x
    [!] Level 1 urgent task
    [-] Level 1 skipped task
    [.] Level 1 on hold task
    [+] Level 1 added task
    [?] Level 1 question task

##Task States - Level 2 (8 spaces)##

        [ ] Level 2 unchecked task
        [•] Level 2 in progress task
        [√] Level 2 completed task
        [!] Level 2 urgent task

##Task States - Level 3+ (12+ spaces)##

            [ ] Level 3 unchecked task
            [•] Level 3 in progress task
            [√] Level 3 completed task
            [!] Level 3 urgent task

##Priority Levels##

[!0] Critical priority - drop everything
[!1] High priority - do soon
[!2] Medium priority - normal importance
[!3] Lower priority - when time permits

    [!0] Nested critical priority
    [!1] Nested high priority
        [!2] Deep nested medium priority

##List Styles - Dash##

- Dash list item 1
- Dash list item 2
    - Nested dash item level 1
    - Another nested dash
        - Deep nested dash level 2
            - Even deeper dash level 3+

##List Styles - Arrow##

-> Arrow list shows flow
-> Another arrow item
    -> Nested arrow level 1
        -> Deep arrow level 2

##List Styles - Thick Arrow##

=> Thick arrow for emphasis
=> Strong point here
    => Nested thick arrow
        => Deep thick arrow

##List Styles - Numbered##

1. First item
2. Second item
3. Third item
    1. Nested first
    2. Nested second
        1. Deep nested
        2. Another deep

##List Styles - Sub-numbered##

1.1. Sub-numbered item
1.2. Another sub-item
1.2.1. Triple sub-numbered
    2.1. Indented sub-numbered
    2.2.3. Complex sub-numbering

##List Styles - Asterisk##

* Asterisk item 1
* Asterisk item 2
    * Nested asterisk
        * Deep asterisk

##List Styles - Bullet##

• Bullet item 1
• Bullet item 2
    • Nested bullet
        • Deep bullet

